.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-9-4::.
There 4 different types of food: lime, potato, banana, corn
The people have 4 different jobs:  designer, librarian, manager, police-officer
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, crime, superhero, time-travel
4 different pets are kept: cat, goldfish, hamster, horse
 1. the person eating corn is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1
 2. the person watching comedy movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching crime movies##5
 3. the person eating potato and the police-officer have different parity positions##9
 4. the manager is on the left or right of the owner of the hamster##3
 5. the manager is not the person watching comedy movies##6
 6. the designer and the person watching crime movies have the same parity positions##9
 7. the designer is somewhere between the owner of the horse and the person eating corn##7
 8. the police-officer is not to the left of the person watching superhero movies##8
 9. the person eating lime is not the person watching crime movies##6
10. the person eating banana is not to the right of the librarian##8
11. the owner of the goldfish is not the person eating corn##6
12. the designer and the person watching crime movies have the same parity positions##9
13. the designer is the person eating potato##1
14. the librarian is somewhere to the right of the police-officer##5
15. the owner of the cat is not to the left of the person eating lime##8
16. the person eating corn is on the left of the designer##1
17. the person watching superhero movies is not the owner of the cat##6
18. the owner of the hamster is somewhere to the left of the person eating potato##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2        |    3     |      4      |
| Beverage      | lime | corn       | potato    | banana    |
| Job           | manager     | police-officer | designer | librarian   |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero   | comedy         | crime    | time-travel |
| Pet           | goldfish    | hamster        | cat      | horse       |

