 6. the fan funk is somewhere between the person watching disaster movies and the person driving the scooter##7
 7. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the fan soul##1
 8. the person drinking milk is somewhere to the right of the person drinking soy-milk##5
 9. the fan funk is not to the right of the person driving the taxi##8
10. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person watching musical movies##3
11. the fan funk is somewhere to the left of the person drinking coffee##5
12. the fan dubstep is somewhere to the right of the person drinking fanta##5
13. the fan dubstep is on the far left or far right##3
14. the person watching mystery movies is not the person drinking soy-milk##6
15. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
16. the person driving the taxi is somewhere to the right of the person driving the scooter##5
