 3. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
 4. the person who's hobby is puzzles and the person driving the helicopter have the same parity positions##9
 5. the person driving the helicopter is somewhere to the right of the person eating radish##5
 6. the person who likes coral is not the person driving the trike##6
 7. the person who's hobby is skydiving is not to the right of the person who likes lilac##8
 8. the person who's hobby is photography is somewhere to the left of the person driving the roller##5
 9. the person who's hobby is gardening and the person who likes pink have different parity positions##9
10. the person eating avocado and the person who likes pink have different parity positions##9
11. the person who's hobby is puzzles is not the person driving the trike##6
12. the person who likes coral is not to the left of the person driving the helicopter##8
13. the person eating radish is not to the left of the person eating lemon##8
14. the person who likes purple is on the left or right of the person eating cucumber##3
15. the person eating cucumber is not to the left of the person who likes coral##8
16. the person who likes lilac is not to the right of the person eating lemon##8
17. the person eating avocado is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
